Description: Advanced duplicate file finder and cleaner
 Duplicate Agent is a powerful tool for finding and cleaning
 duplicate files on your system.
 .
 Features:
  * MD5-based duplicate detection
  * Similar file finder (perceptual hash)
  * Duplicate folder finder
  * File system watchdog (real-time monitoring)
  * Scheduled scanning
  * Compression suggester
  * Multi-language support (19+ languages)
  * Safe trash system
  * Beautiful Qt-based GUI
